OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FA man in Pontardawe who was at risk of
OL,7,Fa life-changing diabetes diagnosis,
OL,8,Fsays it was a 'big shock' because he
OL,9,Fwas not suffering from any symptoms
OL,10,Flinked to the disease.
OL,12,FDarren Rix only found out that he had
OL,13,Fpre-diabetes after a routine eye test.
OL,15,FIt's as a leading diabetes charity
OL,16,Fsays Wales is facing a "hidden health
OL,17,Fcrisis" as the country battles an all
OL,18,Ftime high of those with the condition.
