OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FPre-diabetes is when somebody has high
OL,7,Fblood glucose levels, but not high
OL,8,Fenough to be diagnosed with type 2
OL,9,Fdiabetes, but on the path towards it.
OL,11,FSome of the risk factors of type 2
OL,12,Fdiabetes include age, ethnicity,
OL,13,Ffamily history and being overweight or
OL,14,Fobese.
OL,16,FDarren says he was shocked to find out
OL,17,Fhe was a type 2 pre-diabetic and says
OL,18,F"I didn't think I was that obese,
OL,19,Fthere's probably many people out there
OL,20,Fwho don't realise they have got pre-
OL,21,Fdiabetes."
