OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FHe has now been able to reverse his
OL,7,Fdiagnosis, after taking up swimming
OL,8,Fthree times a week and cutting down on
OL,9,Fsugary foods.
OL,11,F"I was really happy, it was like an
OL,12,Faward that I had won personally...the
OL,13,Fwhole industry needs to change to make
OL,14,Fa better life for everyone"
OL,16,FLatest data from Diabetes UK shows
OL,17,Fthat one in five adults in Wales are
OL,18,Fnow living with diabetes or pre-
OL,19,Fdiabetes.
