OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FThe charity says urgent action is
OL,7,Frequired by the Welsh Government to
OL,8,Ftackle the rise in the condition.
OL,10,FDiabetes is one of the leading causes
OL,11,Fof preventable sight loss in people of
OL,12,Fworking age in the UK, and is a major
OL,13,Fcause of lower limb amputation, kidney
OL,14,Ffailure and stroke. There is currently
OL,15,Fno known cure for any type of diabetes.
OL,17,FFigures show that diagnoses of people
OL,18,Fwith the disease in Wales are on the
OL,19,Frise.
