OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FDiabetes UK wants the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fto do following:
OL,9,FDiabetes UK has called on the Cabinet
OL,10,FSecretary for Health and Social Care,
OL,11,FJeremy Miles, to ensure the prevention
OL,12,Fof type 2 diabetes is embedded into
OL,13,Fits "Healthy Weight Healthy Wales
OL,14,Fstrategy".
OL,16,FIn 2023-24 there were 226,575 people
OL,17,Fin Wales diagnosed with the disease,
OL,18,Fup from 212,108 on the previous year.
OL,20,FSome 90% have type 2 diabetes, while
OL,21,F8% have type 1 diabetes.
