OL,3,CMan who was on the road to Type 2
OL,4,Cdiabetes reverses diagnoses
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government said they were
OL,7,Fconcerned about the rising levels and
OL,8,Fadded that "unlike type 1 diabetes,
OL,9,Ftype 2 diabetes can be prevented and
OL,10,Fwe have invested #1 million per year
OL,11,Fto support our prevention programme."
OL,13,F58,906 people in Wales are living with
OL,14,Fundiagnosed type 2 diabetes. Diabetes
OL,15,FUK has called for those to be
OL,16,F"urgently" identified, along with more
OL,17,Finvestment programmes that promote
OL,18,Flifestyle changes.
