OL,6,FThe charity's Director for Wales,
OL,7,FRachel Burr says: "there must be
OL,8,Fbetter care for the hundreds and
OL,9,Fthousands of people living with all
OL,10,Ftypes of diabetes.
OL,12,F"It's also critical that much more is
OL,13,Fdone to find the thousands of people
OL,14,Fwho either have type 2 diabetes or pre-
OL,15,Fdiabetes, but are completely unaware
OL,16,Fof it".
